Package: granian
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, python3-granian, adduser
Description: multi-application systemd supervisor for python3-granian
 Small native supervisor for the Granian Python HTTP server.
 .
 It reads global defaults from /etc/granian, loads each enabled application
 from apps-enabled, and starts one upstream /usr/bin/granian process per app
 under a single systemd service.
